_sText:
Note: Use only latest version !

This is my first, simple map. Humans have to escape from the space station. There is a one secret (easy to find by the way). Enjoy !

Feel free to comment it.

Please report any bugs and errors! 

2018 Update: After 4 years I decided to update my first map ever for CS:S. Fixed some bugs, made it more playable etc.
